{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Smashed to pieces.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then they decided-- the camp wasn't touched too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then they decided we should build a trench in the camp so that we can hide there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So there were specifications, so we dug the trench.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we covered it with boards, and then we should cover it with half a meter of sand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there came about four lorries, big trucks, with sand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they-- the sand was caked, so they brought sieves, and they brought spades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was a commando created, which was called Sand Commando.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They brought it in October, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we left the camp in April-- 18 of April, 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the Sand Commando was active.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were sifting the sand from one corner of the camp to the other corner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Just sifting the sand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The sand never came on this things, for it was registered as Sand Commando that we are just fooling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And nobody found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, in spring-- no, in early, early spring, 1945, they took 300 of our guys and sent them away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I found later that they were sick, and they were sent to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then, to replace them, we got there are some Aryan Poles, and then we got some Aryan Ukrainians who were in the camp of reason probably that they have been a little fair.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "There was never-- there was, I would say, a couple of hundred of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We were originally a thousand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1,000 men who came with the transport from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the bombardments were practically every second week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took some toll in the camp, for it was a tremendously difficult.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
